6. REPORT INTERPRETATION
6.1 Scoring Logic
Healthy Range (65–100): Suggests cognitive functions are within normal limits.

High Risk (<65): Indicates significant markers of cognitive decline. Immediate referral to a neurologist is recommended.

6.2 Treatment Suggestions
The AI generates localized recommendations:

Healthy: Cognitive wellness plans, puzzles, and diet tips.

High Risk: Contact info for Senior Neurologists, MRI/CT scheduling, and support groups.

7. MAINTENANCE & SECURITY
7.1 Data Storage
This version uses LocalStorage. Patient data is stored on the physical machine. To clear data, use the "Logout" button or clear browser cache.

7.2 Code Integrity
Ensure the dict object in the script tag is not modified, as it contains the critical translation mapping for the 15-step diagnostic process.

